<emphasis box="[266,349,1107,1131]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="38">Elytron</emphasis>
wider from apical third to apex; apex one third wider than base. 
<emphasis box="[1076,1129,1108,1131]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="38">Legs</emphasis>
