<emphasis box="[223,293,1179,1203]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="38">Claws</emphasis>
with dorsal blade curved at apex, ventral blade slightly curved, wider than dorsal blade near apical third.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,350,1778]" pageId="17" pageNumber="38">
